-- Ford increases market share in Europe
-- 
-- Tue Apr 15, 2008 11:44am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/04/15/us-ford-europe-sales-idUSN1546111320080415

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Ford Motor Co ( F.N ) said on Tuesday it sold 187,400 vehicles in Europe's main 19 markets in March, increasing its market share to 9.9 percent. 

 The UK was the biggest market for Ford, with sales of 83,460 vehicles. Ford said its sales across all its 51 markets in the region, including Russia and Turkey, were 221,100 vehicles. (Reporting by  Soyoung Kim , editing by Gerald E. McCormick)